=Night of Love With You=

19
00:01:09,020 --> 00:01:11,980
=Episode 23=

20
00:01:18,840 --> 00:01:19,400
Luo Qing.

21
00:01:23,720 --> 00:01:24,720
Mu Nanchen?

22
00:01:25,240 --> 00:01:26,040
What a coincidence.

23
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:27,520
Are you here for dinner?

24
00:01:27,520 --> 00:01:27,880
No.

25
00:01:29,320 --> 00:01:30,480
I'm here to see you.

26
00:01:31,560 --> 00:01:33,920
I thought we made it clear last time.

27
00:01:34,560 --> 00:01:35,600
Mu Nanchen.

28
00:01:35,600 --> 00:01:36,720
You are very nice,

29
00:01:37,040 --> 00:01:39,680
but I only see you as a friend.

30
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:41,440
The person I like is Leng Yehan.

31
00:01:41,440 --> 00:01:43,160
And Leng Yehan also likes me.

32
00:01:43,160 --> 00:01:43,960
Therefore...

33
00:01:43,960 --> 00:01:44,520
You're right.

34
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:46,920
There's no need for a third party
in a relationship,

35
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:49,000
so just let him quit.

36
00:01:49,480 --> 00:01:52,080
I didn't get it.

37
00:01:53,320 --> 00:01:55,040
I went to see Leng Yehan.

38
00:01:55,040 --> 00:01:56,840
I bought Song's Group

39
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:59,400
and promised him to be the CEO

40
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:00,560
as long as he leaves you.

41
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:01,960
He agreed.

42
00:02:02,720 --> 00:02:03,480
Mu Nanchen.

43
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:06,840
Are you out of your mind

44
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:09,720
or suffered too much?

45
00:02:10,720 --> 00:02:11,440
Luo Qing.

46
00:02:15,640 --> 00:02:16,640
Mu Nanchen

47
00:02:16,640 --> 00:02:17,960
