What he said is true.

51
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:29,720
Wait.

52
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:32,480
What's going on with you guys?

53
00:02:35,600 --> 00:02:36,840
When Mu Nanchen

54
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:38,240
made that offer,

55
00:02:38,920 --> 00:02:40,320
I also thought I wouldn't say yes,

56
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:41,840
but I wavered.

57
00:02:42,160 --> 00:02:43,320
I did like you before,

58
00:02:43,720 --> 00:02:45,800
but what I need more
is power and status.

59
00:02:46,040 --> 00:02:47,680
I've been plotting my revenge
for so long,

60
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:49,600
I'm not gonna give up like that.

61
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:52,120
Leng Yehan.

62
00:02:52,280 --> 00:02:53,520
What are you talking about?

63
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:55,240
Well,

64
00:02:56,200 --> 00:02:57,000
