65
00:02:57,960 --> 00:02:59,120
Go back to him.

66
00:03:00,040 --> 00:03:01,560
I also have my own things to do.

67
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:04,640
I'm sorry.

68
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:09,960
Leng Yehan!

69
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:17,120
Leng Yehan!

70
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:18,400
What do you mean?

71
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:19,880
I don't believe you would do this.

72
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:22,080
You were willing to give up
everything you had.

73
00:03:22,080 --> 00:03:22,840
You even...

74
00:03:24,480 --> 00:03:26,240
How could you possibly accept
Mu Nanchen's offer?

75
00:03:26,600 --> 00:03:27,800
What happened?

76
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:29,280
Tell me and we can

77
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:30,360
figure it out together.

78
00:03:34,480 --> 00:03:35,880
Did I not make myself clear?

79
00:03:36,200 --> 00:03:37,800
Nothing happened.

80
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:39,240
It's just that I'm calm now.

81
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:40,760
I realized I did those things

82
00:03:40,760 --> 00:03:41,840
out of compulsion.

83
00:03:42,080 --> 00:03:43,280
I want to go back to the way it was.

84
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,520
What's wrong with that?

85
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:45,080
No.

86
00:03:45,440 --> 00:03:46,480
I know you.

87
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:47,760
You're not like this.

88
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:49,560
You don't know me that well.

89
00:03:51,600 --> 00:03:52,880
Do you know anything about my past?

90
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:55,680
Do you know my obsession
with revenge?

91
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:57,240
You're the one

92
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:58,560
who sabotaged my plan.

93
00:03:58,760 --> 00:03:59,520
You're the one

94
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:01,280
who made me give up everything.

95
00:04:01,600 --> 00:04:02,200
You're the one

96
00:04:03,480 --> 00:04:05,160
who took my meaning away from me.

97
00:04:08,720 --> 00:04:09,960
Don't flatter yourself.

98
00:04:11,200 --> 00:04:12,880
Nothing happened.

99
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:14,800
This is the way I am.

100
00:04:15,200 --> 00:04:16,200
Your arrival

101
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:17,560
is like a pebble

102
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:18,560
thrown into a pond.

103
00:04:18,760 --> 00:04:19,800
I admit there were some ripples.

104
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:23,720
But when the last ripple disappears,

105
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,080
the pond is calm as normal.

106
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:31,240
I have a lot of things to do.

107
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:33,240
What happened before

108
00:04:34,280 --> 00:04:35,200
is in the past.

109
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:36,400
No.

110
00:04:37,640 --> 00:04:38,480
I believe you.

111
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:40,640
You won't do this to me.

112
00:04:42,760 --> 00:04:43,280
Mr. Mu.

113
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,760
Don't forget what you promised me.

114
00:04:47,320 --> 00:04:48,040
Of course.

115
00:04:48,640 --> 00:04:50,000
