116
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:00,480
No.

117
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:02,240
It's impossible.

118
00:05:03,400 --> 00:05:04,840
Something must have happened.

119
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:06,320
He is not like this.

120
00:05:08,200 --> 00:05:08,800
Luo Qing.

121
00:05:09,760 --> 00:05:11,160
Stop fooling yourself.

122
00:05:11,640 --> 00:05:12,480
