148
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:10,320
It's impossible.

149
00:07:11,640 --> 00:07:12,560
Something must have happened.

150
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:13,840
He must have a reason to do this,

151
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:15,880
but I don't have a clue.

152
00:07:16,400 --> 00:07:17,440
Do you

153
